Do I listen to the thoughts I have on my lower days or higher days?
Both seem right. But only in the moment.
Once the moment is gone, the thought seems harsh or misinformed or delusional.
Both are me-Both are valid. But who do I trust?
#thoughts #depression #mentalhealth #anxiety
